descp2: int, RandomState instance or None, optional (default=None) The generator used to randomly select a subset of samples.  If int, random_state is the seed used by the random number generator; If RandomState instance, random_state is the random number generator; If None, the random number generator is the RandomState instance used by `np.random`. Used when ``sample_size is not None``.
